media:group.media:description:
Get yourself a clean, waste-free shave with Henson Shaving! Use code "simon" for 100 free blades: https://bit.ly/3ga5KYF

Clouds come in all sorts of shapes and sizes, and some of them are objectively better than others. In this entirely serious, scientific, and non-biased video I talk about which clouds are great, and which ones can get in the atmospheric bin. If you don't know your cumulus from your cirrus, this video will also help you out.

This video was chosen by my patrons! You can support the channel by becoming a patron at http://www.patreon.com/simonoxfphys

Check out my website! https://www.simonoxfphys.com/
